We identified 223 and 258 articles, respectively, using PubMed filters such as "since 01/01/2000", "human", "adults", "English or French", and "clinical trial/review/guidelines", and Mesh search terms "encephalitis/therapy" and "encephalitis/diagnosis". We also took into consideration articles mentioned in the selected articles, without using filters for publication dates. We identified 38 articles with the search terms "encephalitis and corticosteroid", and 85 articles with "encephalitis and doxycycline" without using the abovementioned filters. We included a total of 210 articles in the literature analysis. 


